Decomposition Colonne Location de 2015 comme 2016¶

In [8]:
lat = []
long = []
city = []
state = []

for i in range(data_2015.shape[0]):
    lat.append(float(data_2015['Location'][i].split(",")[0].split("'")[3]))
    long.append(float(data_2015['Location'][i].split(",")[1].split("'")[3]))
    
    city.append(data_2015["Location"][i].split(",")[3].split(":")[1])
    state.append(data_2015["Location"][i].split(",")[4].split(",")[0].split(":")[1].split("'")[0])
In [9]:
data_2015["Latitude"] = lat
data_2015["Longitude"] = long
data_2015["City"] = city
data_2015["State"] = state

del data_2015["Location"]

Séparation du Data Set en deux Variables Quanti (data[num]) & Quali (data[cat])¶

In [34]:
num = []
cat = []

for elt in data.columns: 
    if data[elt].dtypes == 'object':
        cat.append(elt)
    
    else :
        num.append(elt)

data_num = data[num]
data_cat = data[cat]
